{"tid":1486410,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"出動鬼武者真正義意","createTime":"2019-08-19T00:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:17:09.000Z","uid":221927,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b994bff2bbeed72f89336e58bec933c93d56e9","tid":1486410,"uid":221927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:56:45.000Z","msg":"呢班鬼武者主要目的唔係拉人，亦唔係扮示威者去衝擊，而係要我地變哂捉鬼敢死隊，分化成場運動！<br />\n<br />\n當我地示威者連換衫地方都諗過度過，你估啲狗狗真係咁撚蠢，cos好play將架車停係路邊等你地影，大搖大擺cos住play係正門入狗屋，甚至係記者會入面曲線承認有狗做鬼。咁高調其實為左引導大家將以往及將來嘅勇武行為入落狗狗數，甚至引我地捉鬼(eg機場捉國安)，進一步分化和理非同勇武。引至818一役已經有分化嘅苗頭出現，和理屌人唔散水，大台攞住大聲公叫人捉鬼，勇武屌人覺得自己贏左。<br />\n<br />\n我地走到今日，全賴當初一句｢不分化不督灰不割席｣，雨革會輸係因為我地分化，被政府帶番風向做主導，我地一定唔可以再重蹈覆轍！<br />\n<br />\n鬼啫，我地解放軍都唔驚驚佢？"},{"pid":"08397c7b66b9023ace6984cd00a9dbfdb5b7e43f","tid":1486410,"uid":271157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔好再捉鬼啦......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d43b71f424afc743cf9160033f6ac4b63c1cd27","tid":1486410,"uid":221927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"973f670a050be76696c1611d7020072a2b0701cb","tid":1486410,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"不要捉鬼"},{"pid":"47e8be9ac8c40080a0c1b3ec3d2367ec08a9f3d1","tid":1486410,"uid":79046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:57:59.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「８２３人鏈」<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2dzjyo4yc2sta.cloudfront.net/?url=images.pitchero.com/ui/2245472/image_5ae228ce3a90a.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;h=128&amp;t=square\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2dzjyo4yc2sta.cloudfront.net%2F%3Furl%3Dimages.pitchero.com%2Fui%2F2245472%2Fimage_5ae228ce3a90a.jpg%26w%3D128%26h%3D128%26t%3Dsquare&h=73f103df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n８２３人鏈：香港之路Hong Kon